<p>France and I am anxiously looking forward to the day when we will sail.<br/>Well Mr Sawell will close this short letter but hope to hear from you soon, I shall write again when opportunity arises as this is the last mail leaving Egypt for six weeks on account of our going away.<br/>Kindest regards to the Telegraph frpm<br/>Yours very sincerely<br/>Eric G Hellstrom<br/>634 Bombardier<br/>3rd Battery 1st A.F.A.<br/>Intermediate Base.</p>
